# Substrate RPC module for web3 compatibility

## Project Description
EVM is important in Substrate framework. With EVM, Substrate can be easily compatible with Ethereum ecosystem. Existing module provide the EVM module itself and a lot relevent should be done to fully support EVM in Substrate, specifically to provide rpc proxy with web3 compatability.
This project intents to develop a Substrate RPC module for web3 compatibility.

